FOR 0.1
-------

 * Javadocs

 * Being able to disconnect from the bus (deallocateAddress)

 * Be able to unsubscribe from well known address

FOR 0.2
-------

 * Blocking streams to avoid thread pool starvation on blocking IO
     - note that we also need to do managed blocks when creating the stream
       instances in the first place (eg. new FileInputStream)
     - Look at nio.2 for Java 7 async api

 * A clean way to send a Shutdown message from the bus to all actors

 * Unit tests

 * Migrate Juglr into Jumpr namespace as jumpr.messaging

 * Migrate standard Jumpr classes to jumpr.core
 
 * StructuredMessage template matching for easy message validation
